      "page": 2,
      "paragraph_index": 10,
      "text": "8. This circular is available on the SEBI website at www.sebi.gov.in under the category,\n‘Legal → Circulars’.\nYours faithfully,\nDivya Hamirbasia\nDeputy General Manager\n022-26449293\ndivyah@sebi.gov.in",
